"title": "9121: eternity, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9121",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God alone possesses lasting time, in contrast to the fleeting time of the human race.</p>\n<h2>Eternity from God's perspective</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:4\">PSA 90:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:8\">2PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's eternity is absolute</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:26\">ROM 16:26</a></p>\n<h2>The name of God and eternity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:14-Exod3:15\">EXO 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:33\">GEN 21:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:4\">ISA 41:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:8\">REV 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's eternal attributes</h2>\n<h3>His love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:8\">1JN 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>His righteousness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:6\">ISA 51:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:9\">2CO 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>His wisdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>His power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>Worship of God as eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:25\">JUD 1:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:36\">1CH 16:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:36\">ROM 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's eternal existence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:8\">HEB 13:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:10-Heb1:12\">HEB 1:10–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25-Ps102:27\">PSA 102:25–102:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:6\">HEB 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:4\">PSA 110:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:24-Heb7:25\">HEB 7:24–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17-Rev1:18\">REV 1:17–1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:13\">REV 22:13</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's eternal existence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Eternity and creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:29\">PRO 8:22–8:29</a> <em>Wisdom (personified) is speaking here.</em></p>\n<h2>Eternity and the human race</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:5\">PSA 39:4–39:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:5\">JOB 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:26\">JOB 36:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a></p>",
